---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import WhatsappWidget from '../components/WhatsappWidget.astro';
---

<Layout title="Legal Policies | SEO Ustaad" description="Read the Terms of Service, Privacy Policy, and Refund Policy for SEO Ustaad. We believe in 100% transparency for our premium digital marketing and SEO services." canonicalUrl="https://seoustaad.com/legal/">
    <Header slot="header" />
    
    <div class="hero-orb hero-orb-1"></div><div class="hero-orb hero-orb-2"></div><main class="container py-5 mt-5"><div class="row justify-content-center pt-5"><div class="col-lg-10 text-center mb-5"><span class="tier-badge mb-3 d-inline-block">Compliance</span><h1 class="display-3 outfit mb-3">Legal <span class="text-orange">Policies</span></h1><p class="text-gray">Our transparent operations guidelines, terms of service, and client protection protocols.</p></div></div><div class="row justify-content-center"><div class="col-lg-10"><section id="privacy" class="mb-4"><div class="glass-card p-4 p-md-5"><div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-4"><div class="h2 mb-0 text-orange"><i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i></div><h2 class="outfit h3 mb-0 ms-3">Privacy Policy</h2></div><p class="text-gray mb-0">At SEO Ustaad, we prioritize your data security. We only collect information necessary to provide our digital services. Your data is encrypted and never sold to third parties.</p><div class="pt-3 border-top border-white border-opacity-10 border-opacity-10 mt-4 small text-gray"><i class="fas fa-envelope text-orange me-2"></i> Support inquiries: <strong>support@seoustaad.com</strong></div></div></section><section id="terms" class="mb-4"><div class="glass-card p-4 p-md-5"><div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-4"><div class="h2 mb-0 text-orange"><i class="fas fa-file-contract"></i></div><h2 class="outfit h3 mb-0 ms-3">Terms &amp; Conditions</h2></div><p class="text-gray mb-0">By purchasing a package, you agree to our 1 USD = 300 PKR fixed exchange rate policy. Project timelines vary by package tier (30-180 days). SEO Ustaad reserves the right to adjust strategies based on search engine algorithm updates.</p><div class="pt-3 border-top border-white border-opacity-10 border-opacity-10 mt-4 small text-gray"><i class="fas fa-info-circle text-orange me-2"></i> Fixed Conversion: <strong>1 USD = 300 PKR</strong></div></div></section><section id="refund" class="mb-4"><div class="glass-card p-4 p-md-5"><div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-4"><div class="h2 mb-0 text-orange"><i class="fas fa-undo-alt"></i></div><h2 class="outfit h3 mb-0 ms-3">Refund Policy</h2></div><p class="text-gray mb-0">We offer a 50% refund if requested within the first 7 days of project initiation. No refunds are provided after significant technical or creative work has been completed (e.g., after theme development or SEO audit completion).</p><div class="pt-3 border-top border-white border-opacity-10 border-opacity-10 mt-4 small text-gray"><i class="fas fa-calendar-day text-orange me-2"></i> Request window: <strong>First 7 days</strong></div></div></section><section id="disclaimer" class="mb-4"><div class="glass-card p-4 p-md-5"><div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-4"><div class="h2 mb-0 text-orange"><i class="fas fa-exclamation-triangle"></i></div><h2 class="outfit h3 mb-0 ms-3">Disclaimer</h2></div><p class="text-gray mb-0">SEO Ustaad provides professional estimations for rankings and leads. While we use industry-standard practices, we do not guarantee specific #1 positions on Google as algorithms are beyond third-party control.</p><div class="pt-3 border-top border-white border-opacity-10 border-opacity-10 mt-4 small text-gray"><i class="fas fa-search-dollar text-orange me-2"></i> Target Focus: <strong>Rankings &amp; Lead Estimation</strong></div></div></section></div></div></main><button type="button" class="back-to-top-float" id="backToTopBtn" aria-label="Scroll to top"><i class="fas fa-arrow-up"></i></button><div class="modal fade glass-modal" id="packageDetailsModal" tabindex="-1" aria-labelledby="packageDetailsModalLabel" aria-hidden="true"><div class="modal-dialog modal-dialog-centered"><div class="modal-content glass-card border border-white border-opacity-10 border-opacity-25 rounded-4 text-white"><div class="modal-header border-bottom border-white border-opacity-10 border-opacity-25 p-4"><div class="d-flex align-items-center gap-2"><span class="badge bg-orange bg-opacity-10 text-orange border border-orange border-opacity-25 px-2 py-1 rounded-pill small" id="modalPackageTier">Tier 1</span><h5 class="modal-title outfit fw-bold" id="packageDetailsModalLabel">Package Name</h5></div><button type="button" class="btn-close btn-close-white" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"></button></div><div class="modal-body p-4" id="modalPackageBody"></div><div class="modal-footer border-top p-4"><button type="button" class="btn btn-outline-dark btn-sm px-4 py-2 rounded-pill fw-semibold" data-bs-dismiss="modal">Close</button> <a href="javascript:void(0)" id="modalOrderBtn" target="_blank" class="btn btn-orange btn-sm px-4 py-2 rounded-pill fw-bold">Order Now</a></div></div></div></div><script is:inline src="/script.js"></script>
    
    <Footer slot="footer" />
    <WhatsappWidget slot="widget" />
</Layout>
